function BookingForm(){
    return(
        <form>
            <label htmlFor="res-date">Choose date</label>
            <input type="date" id="res-date"></input>

            <label htmlFor="res-time">Choose time</label>
            <select id="res-time ">
                <option>17:00</option>
                <option>18:00</option>
                <option>19:00</option>
                <option>20:00</option>
                <option>21:00</option>
                <option>22:00</option>
            </select>

            <label for="guests">Number of guests</label>
        </form>
    ) 
}

export default BookingForm;
